// Q&A 设置（FAQ）
"FAQ" = "常见问题";
"Frequently Asked Questions" = "常见问题解答";
"Answers to common questions about using StudyPulse." = "关于使用 StudyPulse 的常见问题解答。";

"How does StudyPulse track my grades?" = "StudyPulse 如何追踪我的成绩？";
"StudyPulse stores all grade data locally on your device as JSON files. You can add scores, rankings, importance levels, and even attach a photo of your graded paper. Grades are organized by subject and can be viewed in trend charts over time." = "StudyPulse 将所有成绩数据以 JSON 文件形式存储在设备本地。您可以添加分数、排名、重要级别，甚至附加批改后的试卷照片。成绩按科目组织，并可通过趋势图表查看随时间的变化。";

"What is HRV and why does it matter for studying?" = "什么是 HRV，为什么它对学习很重要？";
"Heart Rate Variability (HRV) measures the variation in time between heartbeats, reflecting your nervous system's recovery state. A higher HRV generally means better recovery and readiness for focused study. StudyPulse uses a 14-day HRV baseline from Apple Watch to classify your readiness as excellent, normal, or low, and provides personalized study suggestions." = "心率变异性（HRV）测量心跳间的时间变化，反映您神经系统的恢复状态。较高的 HRV 通常表示恢复更好，适合专注学习。StudyPulse 使用 Apple Watch 的 14 天 HRV 基线将您的状态分类为优秀、正常或较低，并提供个性化的学习建议。";

"How do I export my data?" = "如何导出我的数据？";
"Go to Settings > Data Management and tap Export. StudyPulse supports CSV export for grades, mistakes, exams, and comprehensive exams. The exported file can be shared via AirDrop, email, or any other sharing extension on your device." = "前往「设置 > 数据管理」并点击导出。StudyPulse 支持以 CSV 格式导出成绩、错题、考试和综合考试。导出的文件可通过 AirDrop、电子邮件或设备上的任何共享扩展进行分享。";

"Where is my data stored?" = "我的数据存储在哪里？";
"All your data is stored locally on your device in the app's Documents folder. Grade photos and avatar images are saved as separate files. StudyPulse does not upload any of your data to external servers. If HealthKit is enabled, HRV and other health signals are read directly from Apple Health and remain on your device." = "您的所有数据都存储在设备本地的应用 Documents 文件夹中。成绩照片和头像图片保存为独立文件。StudyPulse 不会将您的任何数据上传到外部服务器。如果启用了 HealthKit，HRV 和其他健康信号将直接从 Apple Health 读取并保留在您的设备上。";

"Does StudyPulse sync across devices?" = "StudyPulse 支持跨设备同步吗？";
"Currently StudyPulse stores data locally on each device and does not support iCloud sync. Data backup and transfer between devices must be done manually via CSV export-import or by copying the Documents folder. Cross-device sync is a planned feature for a future update." = "目前 StudyPulse 将数据存储在每个设备的本地，不支持 iCloud 同步。设备间的数据备份和传输需要通过 CSV 导出‑导入或复制 Documents 文件夹手动完成。跨设备同步是未来版本计划中的功能。";

"How do I add a mistake note with photos?" = "如何添加带有照片的错题？";
"Tap the Mistakes tab, then tap the + button to create a new mistake note. Each mistake has four editable sections: Question, Reason, Wrong Solution, and Correct Solution. In each section, you can add a photo (camera or photo library) and OCR will automatically extract text from the image." = "点击「错题」标签页，然后点击 + 按钮创建新的错题。每道错题有四个可编辑区块：题目、原因、错误解答和正确解答。在每个区块中，您可以添加照片（相机或相册），OCR 将自动从图片中提取文字。";

"What education systems does StudyPulse support?" = "StudyPulse 支持哪些教育体系？";
"StudyPulse supports 15+ education systems including: Mainland China (National, Zhejiang, Shanghai), Taiwan, Hong Kong, Singapore, UK (IGCSE, A-Level), IB DP, US (AP, SAT, ACT), GRE/GMAT, and TOEFL/IELTS. You can select your education system in Settings > Profile, and subject full scores will be configured automatically." = "StudyPulse 支持 15 种以上教育体系，包括：中国大陆（全国、浙江、上海）、台湾、香港、新加坡、英国（IGCSE、A-Level）、IB DP、美国（AP、SAT、ACT）、GRE/GMAT 和 TOEFL/IELTS。您可以在「设置 > 个人资料」中选择教育体系，科目满分将自动配置。";

"Can I customize my home dashboard?" = "我可以自定义主页仪表盘吗？";
"Yes! Go to Settings > Appearance & Layout > Home Layout to reorder and toggle dashboard cards. You can enable or disable HRV status, quick actions, trend chart, upcoming exams, recent grades, daily quote, and more." = "可以！前往「设置 > 外观与布局 > 主页布局」重新排列和开关仪表盘卡片。您可以启用或禁用 HRV 状态、快捷操作、趋势图、即将到来的考试、近期成绩、每日金句等。";


